  "content_text": "WCL = Westfield Corporation Limited (after June 2014)\nWFDT = WFD Trust (after June 2014)\nWAT = Westfield America Trust\nWHL = Westfield Holdings Limited (prior to June 2014)\nWFT = Westfield Trust (prior to June 2014)\n## Calculations for examples\nEvent | WHL/WCL | WFT/WFDT | WAT | Calculation description\nAcquisition 1/09/2015 ($10) | 1.638 | 6.022 | 2.34 | Allocate purchase price based on NTA table as at 30 June 2015\n- | - | -0.1619 | -0.109 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between September 2015 and June 2018\nJust before 2018 restructure | 1.638 | 5.8601 | 2.231 | Cost base just before 7 June 2018 restructure.\nEvent | WHL/WCL | WFT/WFDT | WAT | Calculation Description\nAcquisition 1/09/2005 ($6) | 0.4266 | 3.1170 | 2.4564 | Allocate purchase price based on NTA table as at 30 June 2005\n- | - | -1.4016 | -1.4063 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between September 2005 and December 2010\nJust prior 2010 restructure | 0.4266 | 1.7154 | 1.0501 | -\n2010 restructure event | - | x0.59 | - | Make adjustment to WFT\nJust after 2010 restructure | 0.4266 | 1.0121 | 1.0501 | -\n- | - | -0.2690 | -0.1946 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between December 2010 and June 2014\nJust before 2014 restructure | 0.4266 | 0.7431 | 0.8555 | -\n2014 restructure event | x0.737 | x0.533 | - | Make adjustments to WHL and WFT\nJust after 2014 restructure | 0.3144 | 0.3961 | 0.8555 | -\n- | - | -0.2574 | -0.1207 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between June 2014 and June 2018\nJust before 2018 restructure | 0.3144 | 0.1387 | 0.7348 | Cost base just before 7 June 2018 restructure.\nEvent | WHL/WCL | WFT/WFDT | WAT | Calculation Description\nAcquisition 8/4/2012 ($12) | 0.4296 | 8.2200 | 3.3504 | Allocate purchase price based on NTA table as at 31 December 2011\n- | - | -0.0098 | -0.0848 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between April 2012 and June 2014\nJust before 2014 restructure | 0.4296 | 8.2102 | 3.2656 | -\n2014 restructure event | x0.737 | x0.533 | - | Make adjustments to WHL and WFT\nJust after 2014 restructure | 0.3166 | 4.3760 | 3.2656 | -\n- | - | -0.2574 | -0.1207 | Subtract deferred tax amounts between June 2014 and June 2018\nJust before 2018 restructure | 0.3166 | 4.1186 | 3.1449 | Cost base just before 7 June 2018 restructure.\nTransaction | WCL | WFDT | WAT\nJune 2014 Scentre/Westfield Group Restructure | WCL after restructure = WHL before restructure × 0.737 | WFDT after restructure = WFT before restructure × 0.533 | No change\nTransaction | WHL | WFT | WAT\nDecember 2010 Westfield Retail Trust Restructure | No Change | WFT after restructure = WFT before restructure × 0.59 | No change\n## Net Tangible Assets and Deferred Tax Distributions\nStart Date | End Date | WCL | WFDT | WAT\n31-Dec-17 | 7-Jun-18 | 21.40% | 45.80% | 32.80%\n30-Jun-17 | 30-Dec-17 | 20.25% | 47.53% | 32.22%\n31-Dec-16 | 29-Jun-17 | 19.99% | 45.96% | 34.05%\n30-Jun-16 | 30-Dec-16 | 19.55% | 49.35% | 31.10%\n31-Dec-15 | 29-Jun-16 | 17.98% | 50.99% | 31.03%\n30-Jun-15 | 30-Dec-15 | 16.38% | 60.22% | 23.40%\n31-Dec-14 | 29-Jun-15 | 13.48% | 66.67% | 19.85%\n30-Jun-14 | 30-Dec-14 | 12.63% | 75.79% | 11.58%\n31-Dec-13 | 29-Jun-14 | 10.70% | 71.88% | 17.42%\n31-Dec-17 | 7-Jun-18 | 21.40% | 45.80% | 32.80%\n30-Jun-17 | 30-Dec-17 | 20.25% | 47.53% | 32.22%\n31-Dec-16 | 29-Jun-17 | 19.99% | 45.96% | 34.05%\n30-Jun-16 | 30-Dec-16 | 19.55% | 49.35% | 31.10%\n31-Dec-15 | 29-Jun-16 | 17.98% | 50.99% | 31.03%\n30-Jun-15 | 30-Dec-15 | 16.38% | 60.22% | 23.40%\n31-Dec-14 | 29-Jun-15 | 13.48% | 66.67% | 19.85%\n30-Jun-14 | 30-Dec-14 | 12.63% | 75.79% | 11.58%\n31-Dec-13 | 29-Jun-14 | 10.70% | 71.88% | 17.42%\nStart Date | End Date | WHL | WFT | WAT\n30-Jun-13 | 30-Dec-13 | 6.72% | 73.82% | 19.46%\n31-Dec-12 | 29-Jun-13 | 5.36% | 75.51% | 19.13%\n30-Jun-12 | 30-Dec-12 | 4.71% | 75.41% | 19.88%\n31-Dec-11 | 29-Jun-12 | 3.58% | 68.50% | 27.92%\n30-Jun-11 | 30-Dec-11 | 3.96% | 68.32% | 27.72%\n31-Dec-10 | 29-Jun-11 | 4.04% | 67.27% | 28.69%\n20-Dec-10 | 30-Dec-10 | 3.15